Interface VeritasSubdisk

All Superinterfaces:
DiskPartition, LogicalDevice, LogicalElement, ManagedElement, ManagedSystemElement, ModelObject, java.io.Serializable, StorageExtent
public interface VeritasSubdisk
extends DiskPartition

Veritas subdisk is part of VM disk which can be divided into several subdisks. Each subdisk represents a contiguous block of physical disk space.
